---

<BaseLayout
  title="When Global Teams Should Use HubSpot for Japan Market Entry | Consilegy"
  description="HubSpot is a strong fit for global teams entering Japan when already in use and properly configured. The key question is not whether to use it, but what to configure before relying on it."
